2002-08-23 23:40  sven

	* CHANGES: [no log message]

2002-08-23 23:39  sven

	* proc/application.class: call_single(): Invoke __call_sub() if
	event contains a caller.

2002-08-23 23:38  sven

	* proc/event.class.php: set_caller(): Store caller to new member
	variable 'caller' instead of inserting a new event that calls
	application::__call_sub(). Calling __call_sub() is now done in
	application::call_single(). set_next() can now be used after a
	set_caller () for the same event without messing up the batch.

2002-08-23 23:11  sven

	* CHANGES, admin_panel/formviews.php: form_safe(): Renamed to
	form_cache().

