2002-05-04 17:52  sven

	* admin_panel/tk/dbisearch.php: tk_dbisearch_has_result(): Didn't
	notice if nothing was found (TK_DBISEARCH_NOT_FOUND was never
	returned). - fixed.

2002-05-04 16:40  sven

	* admin_panel/tk/dbisearch.php: tk_dbisearch_query: New class
	replaces rat tail of arguments.
	
	tk_dbisearch(): Only take a single argument containing a
	tk_dbisearch_query object. New argument 'limit' reduces the number
	of records returned. New argument 'offset' specifies the offset of
	the limited result set.
	
	_tk_dbisearch_create_query(): New function creates an SQL query for
	a form element. This code was moved out of tk_dbisearch() to reduce
	the function size.
	
	tk_dbisearch_get_query_object(): New function returns the last
	tk_dbisearch_query object, so it can be reused for browsing etc.
	
	tk_dbisearch_get_resultsize(): Function removed. Access the query
	object's 'size' variable for the number of total records that match
	the query (unlimited).

2002-05-04 14:02  sven

	* text/xml/template.class: Function comments added.
	
	fetch_tree(): Display full path if file doesn't exist.

2002-04-29 21:50  sven

	* doc/tutorial/de/: 05_form_edit.php, 06_list.php,
	07_form_create.php, 08_delete.php, 09_delete_group.php: Ported to
	new version of the library.

2002-04-29 19:56  sven

	* CHANGES: [no log message]

2002-04-29 19:33  sven

	* admin_panel/tk/dbisearch.php: tk_dbisearch(): New argument
	'limit' specifies the maximum number of entries to return in the
	result set. If limit is not specified all entries are returned.
	'offset' specifies the offset of the limited result window. The
	default is 0.
	
	tk_dbisearch_get_resultsize(): New function returns the number of
	entries in a result set.

2002-04-29 19:30  sven

	* cursor/: cursor.class.php, sql.class.php: size(): New function
	returns number of entries in set.

