	* admin_panel/admin_panel.class: Forgot to include new file
	records.php - fixed.

2001-05-10 05:18  sven

	* dbi/dbobj.class: dbobj(): Checked if row had object reference
	instead of checking if a reference was defined using set() - fixed.

