	* admin_panel/: admin_panel.class, list_append.php, records.php,
	tk/dbisearch.php: Update/delete widgets now use the simplistic form
	handler interface.

2001-05-10 03:55  sven

	* admin_panel/: README, admin_panel.class, tk/dbisearch.php: Form
	handler interface simplified. Handlers must be packed into an own
	class which must be registered using admin_panel::add_fh_set().

2001-05-10 02:22  sven

	* admin_panel/admin_panel.class: show_mime_image(): Function was
	broken - fixed.

2001-05-10 02:21  sven

	* dbi/dbobj.class: dbobj(): Data cache didn't take care of fields.
	If something else than '*' is specified for $fields, ',is_local' is
	appended to the string (or we won't find the object.)

