	set_ref().

2001-05-05 05:31  sven

	* admin_panel/tk/tree_edit.php: Functions now find references
	('id_parent', 'id_last', 'id_next') on their own and must not be
	added to the argument array.  The toolkit is now independent from
	language definitions. txt_* arguments must now contain the real
	message. Argument 'txt_unnamed' needs the name of unnamed nodes.

