2001-04-06 23:29  sven

	* dbi/dbobj.class: DBOBJ(): More references used to avoid copying
	of object data. New argument $fields allows to specify the fields
	to read from an object. This way you don't need to fetch a whole
	image of you just need to know the mime type.

