	* dbi/dbobj.class: assoc () bug fixed. Query was empty.

2000-10-13 14:16  sven

	* dbi/dbundo.class: Class layout for undo functionality.

2000-10-12 17:38  sven

	* dbi/dbobj.class: Removed return.

2000-10-12 16:51  sven

	* dbi/dbobj.class: Now returns *every* found object. See
	$this->active and $this->inactive.

2000-10-11 19:50  sven

	* admin_panel/tk/treeview.class: move(): More verbose error message
	if id_next is illegal.

2000-10-11 15:57  sven

	* dbi/dbi.class: Added double-linked list support. Define back- and
	forward references with the new function set_listrefs ($table,
	$id_last, $id_next).

