	* admin_panel/tk/treeview.class: Root node (id == 1) now also
	viewable.

2000-10-10 21:16  sven

	* admin_panel/tk/treeview.class: Added support for different
	highlightning colors.

2000-10-09 22:36  sven

	* dbi/dbobj.class: Accidently used DBOBJ->is_local to mark the
	object 'local'. DBOJB->found_local is now used to determine if the
	object was *found* local.

