	* dbi/dbwrapper.class: It's checked again if the file is already
	included. This time the nice way using 'return'.

2000-09-11 13:02  sven

	* admin_panel/tk/treeview.class, dbi/dbi.class,
	dbi/dbifilemapper.class, dbi/dbobj.class, dbi/dbwrapper.class,
	admin_panel/admin_panel.class: New directory structure. local/ is
	sorted by languags.All pathes changed.

