	* INSTALL: HOWTO install the php scripts outside the webservers.

2000-09-11 12:12  sven

	* dbi/README: Out of date and removed.

2000-09-10 14:54  sven

	* admin_panel/README: Out of date documentation removed.

2000-09-09 13:18  sven

	* admin_panel/admin_panel.class: Security fix. Uploaded files must
	now reside in '/tmp' or '/usr/tmp'.

2000-09-01 02:58  sven

	* admin_panel/tk/treeview.class: Display of double linked siblings'
	order now fully supported if the according references' names to the
	next and last sibling are given at object construction.  New
	function move() supports moving branches.

2000-09-01 02:57  sven

	* dbi/dbi.class: New function traverse_refs_from ($table, $id,
	function) reads out the specified row and calls $function ($table,
	$row_array). Then it jumps to the row in the row it references and
	does the same again. Primary keys and references must be specified
	using set_primary() and set_ref() before.

2000-09-01 02:53  sven

	* admin_panel/admin_panel.class: Background color of html tables'
	cells now set in each cell to get borders between them when using
	MS Internet Exploder.  Code which was generating <TD> tags has been
	replaced by function calls to open_cell() and close_cell().

2000-08-16 03:19  sven

	* admin_panel/admin_panel.class: Database results now referenced by
	result handle, not the database wrapper.  Public variable 'mark_id'
	added for higlightning single records in views.  CELLSPACING and
	CELLPADDING of 2 added to HTML tables.	_path_from() added to
	correct the local $path array when calling views from views. 
	Confirm() box added.  Deletion of referencing tables now default. 
	Font color can be specified for msgbox().  show_ref() displays
	column contents of referencing rows in any (other) table.  Boolean
	radio widget truefalse() added.  Lots of comments added.

2000-08-16 03:00  sven

	* dbi/dbwrapper.class: Debug mode off.

2000-08-16 03:00  sven

	* admin_panel/tk/treeview.class: Double linked list support added
	to enable free ordering with view().

2000-08-16 02:57  sven

	* dbi/dbi.class: Useless inclusion test removed.  Reference support
	added. New functions set_ref() and set_primary().  multi_delete()
	deletes a table and referencing tables.  column() fetches a column.
	 Comments added.

